stages of development: HbA (α2β2) · HbA2 (α2δ2) · HbF/Fetal (α2γ2) · HbE Gower 1 (ζ2ε2) · HbE Gower 2 (α2ε2)
pathology: HbH (β4) · HbS (α2βS2) · HbC (α2βC2)







